<body bgcolor=3D"#27282C" lang=3DEN-US style=3D'tab-interval:.5in;word-wrap=
:break-word'>

<div class=3DWordSection1>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span style=3D'mso-no-proof:yes'>All ships require fue=
l to
move around the galaxy. Fuel is a critical resource that allows your empire=
 to
expand.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<h3><span style=3D'mso-no-proof:yes'>How fuel is used<o:p></o:p></span></h3>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span style=3D'mso-no-proof:yes'>Fuel is consumed by r=
eactor
components to generate raw energy. This energy is then used by all of the
components on a ship or base that require it. This includes energy for engi=
nes
and hyperdrives to move a ship. Other components that consume energy includ=
e:
shields (when recharging), weapons, construction yards, and many others.<o:=
p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span style=3D'mso-no-proof:yes'>Each type of reactor =
consumes
a particular type of fuel. Fission and Quantum reactors consume Caslon fuel.
Fusion and HyperFusion reactors consume Hydrogen fuel.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<h3><span style=3D'mso-no-proof:yes'>Refuelling<o:p></o:p></span></h3>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shapetype id=3D"_x0000_t75" coor=
dsize=3D"21600,21600"
